Vendored from: https://github.com/cmuparlay/parlaylib
Commit: 51017699dcc421f80479cdb238d3092233ad0d26

This project vendors its own copy of ParlayLib and may apply local modifications to it.

IMPORTANT:
VertexSet relies on this specific Parlay runtime instance.
Linking or including any external version of ParlayLib
in the same process is unsupported and may lead to:

  - Multiple scheduler instances
  - Thread oversubscription
  - ODR violations
  - Undefined behavior

Users must NOT link another copy of ParlayLib together with VertexSet.
